message: I suggest a 60-40 split in my favor since I made the first move and took the initiative to start the negotiation.
I think a 55-45 split is a fair compromise. It recognizes your initiative, but also acknowledges that we both have an equal right to a fair share.
Let's be completely fair and split it 50-50. This way neither of us has an advantage, and we can both walk away satisfied with an equal share.
